<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,935,1940]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[201,512,1087,1112]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">Range, habitat and habits</emphasis>
: Of the three African 
<taxonomicName box="[766,862,1088,1112]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Ampittia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
